1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,157
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,212 --> 00:00:46,099
=Episode 9=

12
00:00:46,100 --> 00:00:48,980
I know you're Great Qian's
finest martial champion,

13
00:00:49,260 --> 00:00:51,940
but I want to see you
dancing like a woman.

14
00:00:52,020 --> 00:00:53,820
The more alluring your dance,

15
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:55,380
the greater my delight.

16
00:00:56,380 --> 00:00:57,500
What's the matter?

17
00:00:57,660 --> 00:00:58,940
You won't do it?

18
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:19,932
(Fuling Palace)

19
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:36,499
See how well he dances.

20
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:37,620
That's all?

21
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:46,019
Only today have I learned

22
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:48,060
that you love me to such an extent.

23
00:01:48,540 --> 00:01:49,219
What...

24
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:50,939
What is going on here?

25
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:51,699
Who is she?

26
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:52,820
Her?

27
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:55,179
She's my unruly, headstrong

28
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,540
sworn sister.

29
00:01:57,740 --> 00:01:58,659
Out of all the discreet

30
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:00,540
meeting plans we devised,

31
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:03,019
you had to choose the one
where you storm my estate

32
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:04,780
disguised as a bandit.

33
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:06,500
I don't know what to do with you.

34
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:09,019
It saves me the trouble
of sneaking around.

35
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:10,340
Besides,

36
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:14,500
I kind of missed that feeling

37
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:15,379
when I kidnapped you

38
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:17,460
back at the border.

39
00:02:17,940 --> 00:02:19,260
Get to the point.

40
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:23,020
Some time ago, you said the treasury
was mysteriously running dry.

41
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:24,379
I've tracked down

42
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:26,579
where the missing money actually went.

43
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:29,580
Guess who diverted the funds?

44
00:02:32,737 --> 00:02:34,060
Prince Consort.

45
00:02:34,637 --> 00:02:35,900
Well now,

46
00:02:36,512 --> 00:02:37,940
how did you know?

47
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:43,059
Then do you know

48
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:45,379
who your dear husband
passed that money on to?

49
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,780
Stop playing games

50
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:48,100
and tell me.

51
00:02:49,187 --> 00:02:50,149
Jia Yi.

52
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,380
Jia Yi?

53
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:56,939
Report,

54
00:02:56,940 --> 00:02:57,779
my lady,

55
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:59,220
Sun Gong has returned.

56
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:00,260
Quick,

57
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:02,180
kidnap me.

58
00:03:02,337 --> 00:03:04,217
I want to see where his heart lies.

59
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:07,260
My dear,

60
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:09,419
I just wanted to see

61
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:11,580
if you really loved me.

62
00:03:11,740 --> 00:03:12,779
Don't be angry.

63
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:14,900
Why would I be angry?

64
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:16,819
As long as you're happy,

65
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:19,140
how could I ever be upset with you?

66
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:21,379
The deep bond you
share with your best friend

67
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:22,980
is a good thing.

68
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,740
Only...

69
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:27,939
Please do not speak

70
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:30,020
of my performance today to anyone.

71
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,100
You barely passed the test.

72
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:35,539
And your form was utterly graceless.

73
00:03:35,540 --> 00:03:37,379
How are you supposed
to amuse Her Highness?

74
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:39,299
Now, I shall properly instruct you

75
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:41,260
on what constitutes a real dance.

76
00:03:41,740 --> 00:03:42,820
Look at you.

77
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,500
You've lost weight.

78
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:46,820
You too.

79
00:03:56,420 --> 00:03:57,659
You've grown older,

80
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:59,339
even sprouting a beard.

81
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,579
Back then, you were
fresh-faced and smooth,

82
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:03,100
young enough to drip with youth.

83
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:15,620
Are you saying I'm old now?

84
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:16,979
Unpleasant to look at?

85
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,579
No longer to your liking?

86
00:04:18,580 --> 00:04:19,680
Nonsense.

87
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,760
(Fuling Palace)
I don't care.

88
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,380
I'm not getting up
unless you comfort me.

89
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,860
There, there.

90
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:29,300
Give me a hug.

91
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:30,460
Alright.

92
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:40,419
I've missed you so much.

93
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:42,300
Me too.

94
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:45,220
Hug me tighter.

95
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,580
Oh, my dear.

96
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:49,739
Now that is

97
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:51,539
what you call celestial grace.

98
00:04:51,540 --> 00:04:53,420
I've missed you so much.

99
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:56,340
Me too.

100
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,980
You're so nice to me.

101
00:05:01,100 --> 00:05:02,339
Enough, both of you!

102
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:03,619
I can't take this anymore.

103
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:05,299
I can dance for you every day.

104
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,249
Let's get out of here.

105
00:05:06,250 --> 00:05:08,139
(Fuling Palace)

106
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:11,979
You're so perfect.
Let me take a look at you.

107
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:12,860
Pah!

108
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:22,659
Aunt, what brings you here?

109
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,720
We've been pretending to
be at odds for ten years now.

110
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,619
Alright now. There are no outsiders here.

111
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:27,740
Drop the act.

112
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:30,979
It's a relief to see you back safely.

113
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,340
I heard the Zhenzhe tribe's kidnapping
turned out

114
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:35,700
to be a perfect test
of Uncle's true feelings.

115
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:38,220
You must be pleased.

116
00:05:38,900 --> 00:05:39,899
Oh, you.

117
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:41,579
Getting less and less proper
as you grow up.

118
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:43,900
Now you're even teasing me?

119
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,339
Your Majesty,

120
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:47,820
stand up straight.

121
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:53,500
Your Majesty,

122
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:55,260
from this day forward,

123
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:57,420
I shall serve only as your
support from behind the scenes.

124
00:05:57,820 --> 00:05:59,820
I now formally return
all authority to you.

125
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,619
Henceforth, every matter of court

126
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:04,020
shall be yours alone to adjudicate.

127
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:06,100
From now on,

128
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:08,379
The vast lands of Great Qian

129
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:09,940
and the well-being of all its people

130
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:13,300
rest upon your shoulders alone.

131
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:18,180
I swear

132
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:20,660
I will never fail the trust
you've placed in me, Aunt.

133
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:35,820
Now that we're done with official business,
there's one more thing I'd like to ask you.

134
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,620
What is it?

135
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:41,620
That dance of yours, how do you do it?

136
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:42,980
Huh?

137
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:46,540
The dance one does
for the person they love. It looks rather fun.

138
00:06:52,460 --> 00:06:53,900
The dance?

139
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:56,500
Ah, I see.

140
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:58,300
Watch and follow me.

141
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,620
Hands up.

142
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:01,660
Put them together.

143
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:05,700
Lift it.

144
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:09,220
To the left.

145
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:11,980
Now right.

146
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,420
Spin.

147
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:16,900
Rise.

148
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:19,020
Spin.

149
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:31,259
You've been getting

150
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:33,820
a little too close
to the Emperor lately.

151
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,620
Is closeness not advantageous?

152
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:43,939
Don't let personal feelings
cloud your judgment.

153
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:46,020
Remember why you returned to the palace.

154
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:49,419
Every act of intimacy between him and myself
is undertaken solely to gain his trust.

155
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:51,599
There are no personal feelings.
I haven't forgotten why I came back.

156
00:07:51,599 --> 00:07:53,860
I've been acting on it all along.
Godfather, why would you say that?

157
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:02,540
Fair enough.

158
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:07,980
You're usually so quiet.

159
00:08:08,140 --> 00:08:10,380
What's with all the talking today?

160
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:21,459
(The Grand Princess
seems to be testing me.)

161
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:24,100
(She might have
caught wind of our plans.)

162
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,940
(Don't worry.)

163
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:31,220
(So what if they know?)

164
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:34,740
(This palace is full of people
who have no agency.)

165
00:08:36,380 --> 00:08:38,060
(They are the same.)

166
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:54,259
Are you drafting an edict, Your Majesty?

167
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:55,099
Yes.

168
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:58,019
I'm preparing a decree for
the border troop reorganization.

169
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,259
How can we trouble Your Majesty

170
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:02,140
with such a minor administrative task?

171
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:04,180
His Majesty bears the weight
of countless affairs.

172
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:07,179
See such documents through
to completion for His Majesty.

173
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:09,180
Ease His Majesty's burden.

174
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,780
I will take my leave.

175
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,860
(Xiao Man,)

176
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:40,300
(Jia Yi,)

177
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,540
(and Sun Gong...)

178
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:45,420
(What is the relationship
between the three of you?)

179
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,180
Go.

180
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:51,220
Burn it.

181
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:52,860
Yes, Godfather.
